text: Ðis sant ða landimare ðare twentiwe hiwe at Tissebiri.
Arest ðe cigel marc scheð on nodre andlang stremes oð Gofesdene.
Of ðere twichene on Wilburge imare on ðane grene wei on wermundes trew.
Of wermundes tre adun richt inne ðe imade of ðane miðon anlang stremes on ðane ealde wdeforde on ðare grene wei on neðe heuedstokes.
Of ðanne heuedstocken forð be twelf aceron ðat it comet to wealwege.
Ðannen to suðames forde anlange hegereawe ðat it comet to nodre.
Ðannen forder west on cures rigt.
Ðanne cyrder it norð on poles leage.
Ðannen forð on cnugel lege and on hiclesham.
Of ðane wege anlang hrigces to inpedeforde.
Anlang weges ðat it cumet to funtgeal on ðone herpoð.
Anlang hrygges to ðere litlen lege.
Forð be gemare eft on funtal of fintes hrigce.
Forðer be his imare oð heuedstoccas.
